Name: Celery, 1 Bunch
Description: Crisp, refreshing celery with a clean flavor, perfect for snacking or adding crunch to your favorite dishes.

Name: Strawberries, 1 Lb
Description: While this berry's colorful cousins—the blueberry and red raspberry—are grown on bushes, this bright red fruit comes from vines close to the ground. It's picked when ready to eat, though a strawberry will become a little sweeter if left at room temperature for a day.

Name: Asparagus, 1 Bunch
Description: Fresh asparagus: slender, tender stalks bursting with flavor and crispness, harvested at peak perfection for culinary delight.

Name: Blueberries, 1 Pint
Description: These sweet, tangy and intensely blue berries contain antioxidants such as anthocyanin, as well as anti-inflammatories. It has sweet-tart taste and their unique blue color
